===Etymology===
{{root|en|ine-pro|*reh₁t-}}
From {{inh|en|enm|rode|id=cross}}, {{m|enm|rood|id=cross|t=cross}}, from {{inh|en|ang|rōd||cross}}, from {{inh|en|gem-pro|*rōdō}}, {{m|gem-pro|*rōdǭ||rod, pole}}, from {{der|en|ine-pro|*rōt-}}, {{m|ine-pro|*reh₁t-||bar, beam, stem}}.

Cognate with {{cog|de|Rute||rod, cane, pole}}, {{cog|no|roda||rod}}. Largely displaced by {{m|en|cross}}. More at {{m|en|rod}}.

